posting_body: ['Whisper Sky', '1755 South Beeler Street, Denver, CO, 80247', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 28', 'OR Text', '28', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Upgrade Your Way Of Living', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1372 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Whisper Sky Apartments epitomize Cherry Creek’s sophisticated but casual way of living.', 'Surrounded by a wealth of green space, gorgeous landscaping, and pet-friendly "bark park"—basically the ultimate backyard.', 'Our spacious one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans were originally built as for-sale condos, so each apartment is unique and upgraded; from custom cabinets and granite tile countertops to large windows, electric fireplaces and attached and detached (one or two-car) garages.', "Plus, our incredible amenities package is the lifestyle upgrade you've been searching for.", 'Enjoy the luxuries of the Cherry Creek neighborhood without the price.', 'Features', '- Disposal', '- Microwave', '- Air Conditioner', '- Ceiling Fan', '- Hardwood Floors', '- Washer/Dryer', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Refrigerator', '- Views', '- Window Coverings', '- Dishwasher', '- Electronic Thermostat', '- Large Closets', '- High Ceilings', '- Wheelchair Access', '- Fireplace', '*Amenities may vary and are subject to change at any time', 'Community Amenities', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Covered Parking', '- On-Site Management', '- Pool', '- Courtyard', '- Availability 24 Hours', '- Attached Garages', '- Award Winning Cherry Creek School District', '- Business Center', '- Dog Park', '- Fitness Center', '- Spa/Hot Tub', '- Package Receiving', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Max 2 Allowed | One time Fee $350', 'Rent $35 Breed restrictions apply, please contact for details.', 'RlErdgEB71j']
